settings.description: OH NO CLASSIC WATER LEVELS FROM SMB1 AAAAH,with some things of classic smb3 water levels,enjoy.
Even if this editor seems kinda robust, it's kinda fun trying to build levels under the GBA's limitation. Level's mostly focused on the Triangular Block's mechanics.
No low budget flagpole this time!
Munchers and nipper plants are alive and happily active here.
Easy level and entry-level style of the SMB series. Have fun! :)
Mario and Shergiok go together until Mario pushes Shergiok so that Luigi rescues Shergiok from Alexsam's evil plans.

Mario gets high, and goes under some.. extreme hallucinations. I wonder what Mario's doing with those Bullet Bills at night...
